  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Flip Club: SURVIVAL GUIDE\r\n\r\nIn this kitchen, you are not just a chef;
    you must MANAGE everything to survive the growing madness!\r\n\r\nMANAGE MONEY:
    Every ingredient is an investment. You must complete orders and make a profit
    because the RENT increases exponentially every single day! If you run out of
    cash, it's game over.\n\r\nMANAGE TIME: Customers are impatient. If you take
    too long, you will lose both money and sanity. Watch the grill closely\u2014burnt
    patties are a waste of resources and time!\n\r\nMANAGE SANITY: You are not alone
    in this basement... Your Sanity drains over time and with every failure. If it
    drops below 50%, the world starts to warp, and you'll hear voices from the shadows.
    Reach 0%, and the darkness claims you forever.\n\r\nManage your resources, guard
    your mind, and pay the rent. How many days can you survive the pressure?"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9a14a8a1184c5f14fbce3338ea4d7a35, type: 2}
